description: Experience the finest in contemporary living in this sleek and stylish penthouse duplex where South Boston meets the Seaport. This front facing, corner residence features incredible oversized windows, bringing in tons of natural light as well as skyline views of the Seaport and downtown beyond.  The modern kitchen blends form and function with designer cabinetry, high-end stainless steel appliances, white quartz counter tops and seating for four stools. The layout lends itself wonderfully to entertaining and can be set up in multiple configurations. There is also a powder room on the main level. Upstairs features 2 bedrooms with great storage and more oversized windows.  Beautiful spa-like bathrooms accentuate the overall design driven feel of this contemporary home. One flight up is your spacious private roof-deck perfectly situated in the front corner to take in the city views. A deeded garage parking space finishes things off and completes a true "total package".  Very walkable too!
